sentences: Jean Mikhael Paskalev Skaaden  (born 24 May 1987), better known as Mikhael Paskalev is a Norwegian singer, songwriter and guitarist from Ålesund.
In February 2012, Paskalev was named Årets Urørt for 2012 as the best promising act by by:Larm.
